These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
There 3 different types of food: grapes, plum, pomegranate
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, tea, 7up
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, folk, trance
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, turquise, fuchsia
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
3. the person eating grapes is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking 7up##2
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the fan of trance is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Food         | plum | grapes   | pomegranate   |
| Beverage   | tea     | cola | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | blues    | folk      |
| Color     | turquise     | blood-red      | fuchsia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, bellflower, dahlia
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, tea
City: boston, miami, new-york
3 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig
1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the person who growsrose is the person traveling to miami##1
5. the owner of the frog is between the person drinking coffee and the person who growsdahlia##2
6. the person who growsdahlia is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Flower          | bellflower  | rose     | dahlia     |
| Beverage   | coffee     | tea     | milk      |
| City   | new-york  | miami | boston |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | frog     | goat       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, orange
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, sailing, biathlon
City: paris, liverpool, venice
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, metal, rock
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
2. the fan of gospel is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person traveling to venice##2
3. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
4. the fan of metal is the person eating kale##1
5. the fan of gospel is the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food          | eggplant  | orange     | kale     |
| Sport           | biathlon | badminton  | sailing   |
| City   | paris  | liverpool    | venice |
| Music-Genre           | rock     | gospel | metal |

