.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, cucumber, raspberry
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, chaman, aristoff
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, brown, grey
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, writing, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the person eating raspberry is between the chaman-smoker and the person who likes fuchsia##2
4. the person eating cucumber is the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food    | cherry       | raspberry  | cucumber   |
| Cigar     | chaman    | aristoff  | bluemaster |
| Color     | brown   | grey | fuchsia        |
| Hobby   | traveling | sudoku     | writing      |

