.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cherry, plum
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, mystery, fantasy
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, water
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, analyst, firefighter
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the electrician is between the person drinking water and the person watching fantasy movies##2
3. the person watching western movies is the analyst##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the electrician is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food          | plum    | carrot     | cherry      |
| Movie-Genre         | western | mystery | fantasy |
| Beverage   | water  | cola       | coffee       |
| Job           | analyst     | electrician       | firefighter     |

