.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, whist, chess
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving, sudoku
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, purple, lilac
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, siglo, alhambra
1. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person playing chess is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who likes purple is between the person playing whist and the siglo-smoker##2
4. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1
5. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Game          | whist | backgammon | chess    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | sudoku      | filmmaking |
| Color   | coral   | purple     | lilac        |
| Cigar           | blend      | alhambra       | siglo      |

