The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, d&b, gospel
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, tulip, poppy
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, rowing, rugby
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the fan of d&b is between the person eating radish and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
3. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person eating peach##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
5. the fan of d&b is between the fan of gospel and the person who growsorchid##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | radish      | peach   | artichoke |
