.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, onion, plum
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, cooking, canasta-climbing
City: hannover, liverpool, london
3 different games are played: domino, snooker, canasta
1. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
2. the person eating onion is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person eating onion is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person eating plum##2
5. the person eating onion is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Food      | eggplant       | onion      | plum      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | canasta-climbing | chess      |
| City           | london | hannover     | liverpool |
| Game   | snooker     | canasta          | domino       |

