.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, cola
City: hamburg, hannover, venice
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, swimming, rugby
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, sudoku, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is rugby##2
2. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | almond-milk | cola     |
| City          | hannover   | hamburg      | venice     |
| Sport   | rugby  | skiing      | swimming |
| Hobby     | woodworking | rock-climbing        | sudoku     |

