The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, project-manager, social-worker
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, funk, rock
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, 7up, hot-chocolate
1. the cape-cod house is on the right of the tower house##1
2. the project-manager is between the engineer and the victorian house##2
3. the fan of rock is the tower house##1
4. the fan of funk is the social-worker##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the engineer##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| House       | victorian       | tower       | cape-cod    |
| Job         | social-worker | project-manager | engineer |
| Music-Genre       | funk      | rock         | r&b |
| Beverage   | almond-milk        | hot-chocolate            | 7up  |

