2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
3. the person who growsrose is in the middle##1
4. the person who growsrose is between the person eating strawberry and the person eating artichoke##2
5. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
6. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Sport      | biathlon     | lacrosse | parkour      |
