.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, woodworking, rock-climbing
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike, roller
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, bolivar, oliveros
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, indonesian, spanish
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person driving the roller##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
3. the australian is on the left of the spanish##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person driving the quad-bike and the bolivar-smoker##2
6. the montecristo-smoker is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Hobby      | puzzles | woodworking      | rock-climbing            |
| Transport           | scooter | roller | quad-bike |
| Cigar   | bolivar     | oliveros        | montecristo         |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | australian    | spanish        |

