There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, 7up
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the pilot is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
3. the nurse is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person eating cucumber##2
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Job           | architect | nurse        | pilot       |
| Birthday   | january | april | december |
| Food           | cucumber     | strawberry         | pineapple  |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate  | 7up       | iced-tea  |

