2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the coach##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the fan of indie is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the fan of salsa is the person who growsazalea##1
6. the coach is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Transport      | boat    | skateboard          | airplane |
| Music-Genre          | indie | trance           | salsa        |
| Job           | fisherman | police-officer | coach         |
| Flower   | sunflower    | begonia    | azalea      |

