2. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the owner of the hamster and the person who's birthday is in june##2
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
4. the person eating cherry is between the owner of the hamster and the person eating artichoke##2
5. the owner of the cat is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Food          | potato  | cherry   | artichoke |
| Pet   | hamster  | cat     | fish |
| Birthday   | january | november | june   |
| Hobby     | video-games   | traveling   | card-games      |

