.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-16::.
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, mexican, indian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, aristoff, baccarat
House: art-deco, modern, gothic-revival
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, train, tram
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the baccarat-smoker is between the person driving the boat and the montecristo-smoker##2
3. the indian is on the far left##1
4. the modern house is the person driving the boat##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the japanese##1
6. the japanese is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Nationality       | indian | japanese | mexican |
| Cigar         | montecristo   | baccarat       | aristoff        |
| House       | gothic-revival | art-deco   | modern         |
| Transport   | tram    | train     | boat         |

