.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, electronic, folk
There 3 different types of food: banana, pineapple, cherry
City: rome, marseilles, liverpool
The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, designer, dressmaker
1. the person eating pineapple is between the dressmaker and the person eating banana##2
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the dressmaker##1
3. the fan of electronic is the person traveling to rome##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is the fan of disco##1
5. the writer is the person traveling to marseilles##1
6. the person eating banana is on the right of the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | disco  | folk     |
| Food   | cherry    | pineapple | banana |
| City           | rome        | liverpool   | marseilles  |
| Job     | dressmaker      | designer   | writer |

