The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, july, march
There are 3 different favourite colors: amber, white, purple
House: townhouse, modern, ranch-style
1. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
2. the modern house is on the left of the engineer##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is the townhouse house##1
4. the lawyer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
6. the writer is between the engineer and the person who likes white##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Job           | lawyer   | writer   | engineer |
| Birthday   | march | july   | november     |
| Color   | white     | amber      | purple    |
| House           | townhouse | modern | ranch-style    |

