.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda
There 3 different types of food: pepper, radish, avocado
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, marigold, aconite
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, thriller, mystery
1. the person watching thriller movies is the person who growsaconite##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
3. the person who growsrose is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person eating pepper##2
4. the person who growsmarigold is the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person watching crime movies is between the person drinking milk and the person who growsmarigold##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda     | milk        |
| Food         | radish   | avocado | pepper |
| Flower   | marigold        | rose       | aconite      |
| Movie-Genre           | mystery           | crime    | thriller       |

