.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, april, december
House: cottage, futuristic, victorian
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, blood-red, azure
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, train, tram
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
2. the futuristic house is the person driving the car##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is the person driving the car##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the victorian house is between the person driving the tram and the person who likes blood-red##2
6. the person who likes azure is the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Birthday        | april      | november | december |
| House         | futuristic     | victorian    | cottage        |
| Color       | blood-red | azure   | aquamarine   |
| Transport   | car          | train     | tram       |

 